1
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:09,400
Is it because of Zhou Honghai?

2
00:01:10,319 --> 00:01:11,840
This is my own decision.

3
00:01:12,359 --> 00:01:13,840
It has nothing to do with him at all.

4
00:01:15,439 --> 00:01:16,920
So what is the reason, exactly?

5
00:01:19,120 --> 00:01:20,439
I really don't want to say.

6
00:01:21,640 --> 00:01:22,359
And even if I told you,

7
00:01:22,359 --> 00:01:23,640
