8
00:01:25,079 --> 00:01:26,840
Only the dead can keep secrets.

9
00:01:27,159 --> 00:01:28,200
Offend the Long Group,

10
00:01:28,439 --> 00:01:30,760
and your family and loved ones won't have a good end.

11
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,000
Next,

12
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:34,439
let's start with your little boyfriend Chen Fan.

13
00:01:39,519 --> 00:01:40,560
You'd just think I'm crazy.

14
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,640
I believe you.

15
00:01:42,359 --> 00:01:43,959
I believe whatever you say.

16
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:45,560
I will always,

17
00:01:45,920 --> 00:01:47,680
