18
00:01:48,879 --> 00:01:50,480
I really can't tell you.

19
00:01:50,480 --> 00:01:52,480
There are things I haven't figured out myself.

20
00:01:53,840 --> 00:01:57,640
I just want to hear a reason from you personally.

21
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:00,239
Even if it's,

22
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:07,239
"I have absolutely no feelings for you anymore."

23
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,120
I accept that.

24
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:18,840
As long as you are safe, happy, and joyful.

25
00:02:21,240 --> 00:02:22,039
I accept it.

26
00:02:27,199 --> 00:02:28,479
I feel the same way.

27
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:32,919
But I just ask one thing of you.

28
00:02:35,879 --> 00:02:36,919
About the camcorder matter,

29
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,360
