30
00:02:41,400 --> 00:02:42,080
Okay.

31
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,240
Hello, Ruochu.

32
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,120
It's Chen Fan.

33
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:15,240
The camcorder is fixed.

34
00:03:19,439 --> 00:03:21,240
Why is this video so blurry?

35
00:03:21,240 --> 00:03:22,360
It keeps shaking.

36
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,759
You can tell at a glance it was filmed secretly.

37
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,960
That makes sense then.

38
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:28,240
When the senior from the law firm went to interview

39
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,080
the victims of Long Real Estate's

40
00:03:29,080 --> 00:03:30,560
violent forced demolition last time,

41
00:03:30,879 --> 00:03:32,560
