42
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:34,120
So they filmed it secretly.

43
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:37,120
If that's really the case,

44
00:03:37,439 --> 00:03:38,680
then this video

45
00:03:39,360 --> 00:03:40,360
can definitely overturn the case;

46
00:03:40,360 --> 00:03:41,719
