47
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,479
If we also have a witness...

48
00:03:45,560 --> 00:03:46,800
Where do we find a witness?

49
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:55,680
Hey, look at this.

50
00:03:57,759 --> 00:03:59,159
This circle here, doesn't it look like

51
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:01,520
