52
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:05,400
Yes.

53
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,479
Yes.

54
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:08,479
I was at the scene that day.

55
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:10,439
Those people from the Long Group,

56
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,599
