59
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:16,800
They even beat people up.

60
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:21,079
It makes me angry just bringing it up.

61
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:22,439
Sir,

62
00:04:22,439 --> 00:04:24,319
