63
00:04:24,319 --> 00:04:25,360
It can serve as physical evidence in Long Real Estate's

64
00:04:25,360 --> 00:04:26,879
violent forced demolition case.

65
00:04:26,879 --> 00:04:28,279
If you are willing to testify in court,

66
00:04:28,279 --> 00:04:29,480
and clearly explain everything

67
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,160
you saw and experienced that day,

68
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:33,240
it will surely help the victims of violent forced demolition

69
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,120
seek justice

70
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:36,120
and make the Long Group people pay the price.

71
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,160
But I heard

72
00:04:38,399 --> 00:04:40,199
the people from Long Real Estate are not to be trifled with.

73
00:04:40,600 --> 00:04:41,560
Before,

74
00:04:41,560 --> 00:04:42,920
when residents stood up to them,

75
00:04:43,120 --> 00:04:44,720
their shops were smashed the next day.

76
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,560
What a joke.

77
00:04:46,399 --> 00:04:47,759
Would I be afraid of them?

78
00:04:48,480 --> 00:04:50,439
I've lived for over sixty years.

79
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:52,079
Evil cannot prevail over good.

80
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:54,759
I still understand this principle.

81
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,800
As long as these hooligans

82
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,639
can be sanctioned by the law,

83
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:03,560
then I will go to court to testify.

84
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,360
Would I be afraid of them?

85
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,560
So, Lawyer Sun

86
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:15,040
gave this camcorder to Xu Qiuci

87
00:05:15,240 --> 00:05:17,600
hoping to use her to destroy Long Real Estate's

88
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:18,720
video evidence of forced demolition.

89
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:19,480
That's right.

90
00:05:19,480 --> 00:05:20,839
And Long Real Estate

91
00:05:20,839 --> 00:05:22,439
was previously involved in violent land seizure,

92
00:05:22,759 --> 00:05:24,120
but due to insufficient evidence at the time,

93
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:25,120
they avoided prosecution.

94
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:26,519
If I'm not mistaken,

95
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:28,360
this video is the

96
00:05:28,360 --> 00:05:29,160
only evidence in that case.

97
00:05:29,160 --> 00:05:29,800
Exactly.

98
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,920
If this video were gone,

99
00:05:31,920 --> 00:05:33,879
then Long Real Estate's violent land seizure

100
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:34,839
would have no evidence left.

101
00:05:34,879 --> 00:05:38,079
It would be hard for us to reinvestigate and prosecute.

102
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:40,519
By the way,

103
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:42,480
we also found the old district's

104
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,759
Uncle Tang from Yunmeng Amusement Park.

105
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:45,160
He saw with his own eyes that day

106
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,079
Long's people smashing things.

107
00:05:46,079 --> 00:05:47,120
He handwrote a testimony

108
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,439
and is willing to testify in court.

109
00:05:48,720 --> 00:05:49,800
We have both the witness and physical evidence.

110
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,160
Reopening this case

111
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:52,279
gives us much better odds of winning.

112
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,519
Let me borrow this for a second.

113
00:05:55,079 --> 00:05:56,639
When I was fixing the camcorder, I noticed

114
00:05:56,639 --> 00:05:58,439
the damage marks on the device were very odd.

115
00:05:58,639 --> 00:05:59,120
Look here.

116
00:05:59,639 --> 00:06:00,120
And here.

117
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:01,920
There are obvious signs of being pulled by force.

118
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,839
It looks like it was forcibly pried open.

119
00:06:04,079 --> 00:06:04,959
So I guess

120
00:06:05,319 --> 00:06:06,959
this person doesn't want the case reopened.

121
00:06:07,279 --> 00:06:08,720
He wants the video to disappear forever.

122
00:06:08,959 --> 00:06:11,240
So the mastermind under the most suspicion right now

123
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,360
is Long Real Estate.

124
00:06:12,519 --> 00:06:14,639
If you're willing to investigate,

125
00:06:14,839 --> 00:06:15,920
you might be able to find

126
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:18,160
unusual clues regarding Lawyer Sun.

127
00:06:19,519 --> 00:06:21,480
Okay, we'll start the investigation.

128
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:22,839
If he really is compromised,

129
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:24,040
I absolutely won't tolerate it.

130
00:06:25,519 --> 00:06:28,759
Lawyer Sun is suspended pending police investigation.

131
00:06:28,759 --> 00:06:29,759
I'm completely in the clear.

132
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,720
That's great.

133
00:06:32,079 --> 00:06:33,279
Ruochu, Chen Fan,

134
00:06:33,519 --> 00:06:35,120
you really helped me out big time.

135
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:36,519
I really need to thank you properly.

136
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:37,120
Let's go.

137
00:06:37,319 --> 00:06:38,360
Let's go to a bar to celebrate.

138
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:40,160
I'll pass on the bar.

139
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:46,079
If we're not going to a bar,

140
00:06:46,079 --> 00:06:47,720
I'll take you somewhere nice.

141
00:06:50,879 --> 00:06:51,959
Come on.

142
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:53,160
Let's go, let's go.

143
00:06:53,160 --> 00:06:53,959
Let's go.

144
00:06:57,959 --> 00:06:59,079
No matter what misunderstandings

145
00:06:59,079 --> 00:07:00,519
or barriers exist between us,

146
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,079
I'll be with you to resolve them.

147
00:07:07,240 --> 00:07:07,720
Ruochu.

148
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,199
Here.

149
00:07:08,199 --> 00:07:08,920
This is for you.

150
00:07:09,120 --> 00:07:09,560
Actually,

151
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:10,560
I like this one.

152
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:11,600
She'll drink this.

153
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,759
Thanks.

154
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:23,680
Chen Fan,

155
00:08:24,879 --> 00:08:26,800
once I've investigated everything clearly,

156
00:08:27,680 --> 00:08:29,240
I will definitely confess everything to you.

157
00:08:31,800 --> 00:08:33,200
You and Ruochu haven't made up yet?

158
00:08:33,759 --> 00:08:35,759
What exactly happened between you two?

159
00:08:37,159 --> 00:08:38,480
It's hard to explain right now.

160
00:08:38,840 --> 00:08:40,480
Dating is really complicated.

161
00:08:40,759 --> 00:08:42,840
Much harder than making games or writing code.

162
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,960
Oh, come on.

163
00:08:45,320 --> 00:08:46,519
What were you two chatting about just now?

164
00:08:46,519 --> 00:08:47,440
Horror movies.

165
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,639
I didn't expect Ruochu to have seen so many.

166
00:08:49,639 --> 00:08:50,960
She even suggested I add them to the game.

167
00:08:52,159 --> 00:08:52,759
By the way,

168
00:08:52,879 --> 00:08:53,840
Ruochu also said

169
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:56,120
she got so nervous watching a horror movie once,

170
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,320
that when the ghost appeared,

171
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:58,559
she dumped a whole bowl of popcorn

172
00:08:58,559 --> 00:09:00,320
all over the person next to her.

173
00:09:00,559 --> 00:09:01,559
Funny, right?

174
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,600
It's nothing, nothing.

175
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,279
This clearly happened in my previous life.

176
00:09:22,799 --> 00:09:23,960
How could Ruochu know?

177
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:34,039
Excuse me, excuse me.

178
00:09:34,039 --> 00:09:34,879
What is it?

179
00:09:34,960 --> 00:09:35,720
Don't block the way.

180
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,240
There won't be any food left soon.

181
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:37,840
Oh, it's fine.

182
00:09:37,840 --> 00:09:38,759
It doesn't matter if there's no food.

183
00:09:38,759 --> 00:09:39,840
I can take you out to eat.

184
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,879
You're not trying to hit on me, are you?

185
00:09:43,240 --> 00:09:44,559
You've misunderstood.

186
00:09:44,919 --> 00:09:46,519
You're Su Ruochu's roommate, right?

187
00:09:46,519 --> 00:09:47,360
Have you noticed...

188
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,480
...that Ruochu has been acting weird lately?

189
00:09:49,480 --> 00:09:50,120
Talking nonsense...

190
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:50,919
...saying things...

191
00:09:50,919 --> 00:09:52,320
...that you guys don't understand?

192
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:53,720
Ruochu.

193
00:09:54,879 --> 00:09:56,320
Sorry, give me a second.

194
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:57,759
Hello?

195
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:58,840
It blew up! It blew up!

196
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,840
The game blew up!

197
00:09:59,840 --> 00:10:00,720
Come back quickly!

198
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,879
Um, tomorrow I'll...

199
00:10:01,879 --> 00:10:03,159
...come ask you again tomorrow.

200
00:10:03,159 --> 00:10:04,080
I'll come by tomorrow!

201
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,840
Chen Fan, come look at this.

202
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:14,679
Let me see.

203
00:10:14,679 --> 00:10:15,480
I just uploaded this game...

204
00:10:15,480 --> 00:10:17,679
...to several university intranet FTPs...

205
00:10:17,679 --> 00:10:18,360
...and a few gaming forums.

206
00:10:18,799 --> 00:10:19,639
It's only been three or four hours...

207
00:10:19,879 --> 00:10:21,039
...and downloads have already topped 100,000.

208
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,080
Not bad.

209
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:23,879
Did you send it to Guo Shuai?

210
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:24,679
I did.

211
00:10:24,720 --> 00:10:26,519
He said the guys in the water army groups are going crazy over it.

212
00:10:26,519 --> 00:10:27,720
They're all promoting it spontaneously.

213
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:28,559
I also followed your instructions...

214
00:10:28,559 --> 00:10:30,480
...and on the latest antivirus software...

215
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,519
...installed pop-up ads.

216
00:10:31,519 --> 00:10:32,960
As long as they click that banner ad...

217
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,480
...they can go in and play our game.

218
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,559
Congratulations, Brother Liang.

219
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:37,559
You really made this game a success.

220
00:10:37,559 --> 00:10:38,320
I really didn't expect...

221
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,399
...that one day so many people...

222
00:10:39,399 --> 00:10:40,320
...would play a game I made.

223
00:10:40,320 --> 00:10:41,240
That's amazing.

224
00:10:41,240 --> 00:10:42,720
When users break one million...

225
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,159
...we'll hold a celebration party.

226
00:10:44,159 --> 00:10:44,559
Yeah.

227
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:46,960
Wenjie, from now on...

228
00:10:46,960 --> 00:10:48,639
...if Brother Liang becomes a big shot in the gaming world...

229
00:10:48,639 --> 00:10:50,440
...we can stop running the internet cafe and the club...

230
00:10:50,519 --> 00:10:51,799
...and just follow Brother Liang.

231
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:56,240
Oh, right.

232
00:10:56,240 --> 00:10:57,960
Tell me how you did this.

233
00:11:00,759 --> 00:11:02,720
Brother Liang and Chen Fan are getting more and more impressive.

234
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,720
While I only know how to do the accounts.

235
00:11:05,279 --> 00:11:06,759
I can't keep up with them anymore.

236
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:10,120
Am I useless to them now?
